--
-- After this migration:
--   - M2-S6-C1 (Mortgage Lending) has 10 of 10 scenarios loaded.
--   - Section 6 is 1 of 6 categories complete.
--
-- No schema changes. The market_indicator_analysis field type and the
-- six M2-S6 categories were created in migration 017.
-- Section-level defaults from migration 017:
--   classification_options = ['Improving','Stable','Declining','Market-Dependent']
--   min_rationale_chars    = 20
--   context_labels_by_category[M2-S6-C1] = 'Lending Context'
-- These are repeated explicitly in each field_options_override for
-- self-describing scenario rows.
