-- Tables array shape:
--   Every scenario stores its indicator data table inside a
--   one-element 'tables' array, even when the source artifact had a
--   single cols/rows pair. This standardizes the JSONB shape across
--   M1–M6 (later modules use multi-element tables arrays for genuinely
--   multi-dataset scenarios).
--
-- Idempotency: this migration runs once and is recorded in the
