hree designations - Increasing, Stable, or Declining - and Stable is correct when indicators hover near equilibrium. The BMW employment note tests whether students can classify a background factor as Stable rather than Improving.", "classification_options": ["Improving", "Stable", "Declining", "Market-Dependent"], "min_rationale_chars": 20}'::jsonb,
