. A market in transition - where indicators are moving but haven''t settled into a new range - calls for nuanced analysis. The interest rate factor tests whether students can connect macro data to local market impact. Critically, stable employment should NOT be cited as an active improving factor when it is merely the absence of a negative.", "classification_options": ["Improving", "Stable", "Declining", "Market-Dependent"], "min_rationale_chars": 20}'::jsonb,
